25 November 2002   V1-4
      This new version has been updated to support orbit predictions 
      within the TCC. The calling interface is the same but the library
      includes one new routine - slaNutc80. 

17 December 2003   V1-5
      Changes for the port to GEM8.5 (EPICS 3.13.9).

06 July 2004       V1-6
      Updated routines from PTW for better handling of asteroids/comets.
      New files epv.c and plantu.c added plus upgrades to plantu.c and
      pertue.c 

03 January 2006   V1-6-1
      Modified dat.c to account for leap second 

11 January 2006   V1-6-2
      Modified slalibInstall to allow compiling for EPICS releases other
      than GEM8.5

16 January 2007 V1-9
      Updated routines from PTW.
      New files c2i.c c2ipa.c c2ipad.c c2ipas.c c2iqk.c c2iqkz.c 
         eo.c eors.c era.c fw2m.c fw2xy.c g2ixys.c gst.c i2c.c i2cqk.c 
         i2o.c i2opa.c i2opad.c i2opat.c i2oqk.c int2in.c nu.c nu00a.c 
         o2i.c o2iqk.c pfw.c pncio.c pneqx.c pomom.c s.c sp.c

29 December 2008 V1-9-1
      Modified dat.c to account for leap second 

